::Feline::

She watched in facination as Zardus worked on the femme on the table. 
She didn't understand when Zardus metioned he had a similar program 
like that of the femmebot's.  She only knew that such an advanced 
program would be useful to her.  She wanted it, but would have to 
wait. But she would get it. She looked at the monitor. "She's out 
totally.  No sighs of life other than the spark still working. What's 
that board going to do?"
